{{Quote|You will stop this at once. Otherwise, I will declare a state of war to exist between the Ishori Confederene and the New Republic.|[[Av'muru]], to [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]]|<ref name="VotF">''[[Vision of the Future]]''</ref>}}
The '''Ishori Confederene''' was the region of space containing [[Isht]]. It was represented in the [[New Republic Senate/Legends|New Republic Senate]] by [[Ghic Dx'ono]]. Its neighbors included the sectors which contained [[Iphigin]] and the [[Diamal]]a homeworld.

